history.content: Are you looking for tips on how to build a great resume? Then this is the perfect place for you! UPE will be holding a resume workshop on 12 Oct (Tue) from 5:10-6:30PM over Zoom (link: https://berkeley.zoom.us/j/95700548505?pwd=QXpzOXRWRHVPUHduckRXWEJONndiQT09 Password, if prompted: 537470). The first portion will be general advice on how to build a resume. Afterwards, we will have breakout rooms for 1:1 resume critiques where you can get *personalized help* on your own resume!
